WEBVTT

00:09:57.407 --> 00:10:00.499
and he described them as a distinct group,

00:10:00.523 --> 00:10:02.999
inferior and beastly.

00:10:04.391 --> 00:10:06.770
Never mind that in that precolonial time

00:10:06.794 --> 00:10:10.746
some of the most sophisticated cultures
in the world were in Africa.

00:10:12.176 --> 00:10:15.443
Why would this guy make this claim?

00:10:16.779 --> 00:10:19.102
Turns out, it helps to follow the money.

00:10:19.859 --> 00:10:22.803
First of all, Zurara was hired
to write that book

00:10:22.827 --> 00:10:25.082
by the Portuguese king,

00:10:25.106 --> 00:10:26.946
and just a few years before,

00:10:26.970 --> 00:10:29.075
slave traders --

00:10:29.099 --> 00:10:30.406
here we go --